HTML5 / CSS3

JavaScript

Responsive UI with glassmorphism and animations

Model Architecture:

Conv2D (32) â” ReLU â” MaxPooling
Conv2D (64) â” ReLU â” MaxPooling
Flatten â” Dense(128) â” Dropout(0.5)
Output: Dense(num_classes) with Softmax

ğŸ† Accuracy

Trained over 10 epochs, achieved high accuracy (~95%+) on validation set.

âš™ï¸ How to Run Locally

1. Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/your-username/plant-disease-detector.git
cd plant-disease-detector

2. Setup Environment

pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Prepare Dataset

Download the PlantVillage dataset and place it in:

data/PlantVillage/

4. Train the Model (Optional)

python train_model.py

This saves plant_disease_model.h5

5. Run the App

python app.py

Open browser at http://127.0.0.1:5000

